  "description": "CIS iOS/iPadOS 26 Benchmark v1.0.0 Apple Intelligence and Siri controls for ADE/Corporate devices (DDM - supervised only). \n\nExternal Intelligence Settings: block ChatGPT/third-party AI integration and sign-in (REPLACE: allowedworkspaceids placeholder with real org GUID if enabling approved workspace access, or remove if not used). (Change Allow Sign In: Allowed [Enabled external intelligence integrations setting]\n\nIntelligence Settings: block Visual Intelligence, Notes transcription/summary (CIS 3.10.2), Mail summary/smart replies (CIS 3.10.3), Safari AI summary, Genmoji, Image Playground, Image Wand, Personalized Handwriting; Writing Tools intentionally allowed (deviation from CIS 3.10.4); force on-device dictation and translation. Siri Settings: disable Siri entirely, block while locked (CIS 3.2.1.2), block user-generated content learning, force profanity filter.",
